00:13:00.474 --> 00:13:02.845
(Music)

00:13:02.869 --> 00:13:04.491
AG: If you work independently,

00:13:04.515 --> 00:13:07.243
you can decide where to bring
those core parts of yourself

00:13:07.267 --> 00:13:08.521
into your job.

00:13:08.545 --> 00:13:10.762
But that's a lot harder if you have a boss

00:13:10.786 --> 00:13:13.279
who isn't on board
with your image of your job.

00:13:13.303 --> 00:13:16.464
And even if your boss is supportive,
what about everyone else?

00:13:17.190 --> 00:13:20.968
Could there be a whole organization
where people can craft their own jobs?

00:13:20.992 --> 00:13:23.182
Where they get to be that self-directed?

00:13:23.206 --> 00:13:26.620
DP: That's our default setting:
autonomous and self-directed.

00:13:26.644 --> 00:13:30.745
And so I think what we have to do
is build organizations